1
00:00:24,560 --> 00:00:26,040
As for the rumor-monger,

2
00:00:26,080 --> 00:00:28,680
our school is discussing how to deal with them.

3
00:00:28,760 --> 00:00:29,760
Rest assured.

4
00:00:29,800 --> 00:00:31,560
We will give Zixi

5
00:00:31,560 --> 00:00:33,680
and you two an explanation as soon as possible.

6
00:00:33,680 --> 00:00:35,080
Thank you for your trouble.

7
00:00:35,080 --> 00:00:36,960
This person is really awful.

8
00:00:36,960 --> 00:00:38,160
That's true.

9
00:00:39,160 --> 00:00:40,160
Oh, right.

10
00:00:40,800 --> 00:00:41,800
May I ask,

11
00:00:42,040 --> 00:00:44,600
why is she targeting our Zixi?

12
00:00:45,080 --> 00:00:49,000
It might have something to do with her live stream.

13
00:00:49,920 --> 00:00:51,440
Live stream?

14
00:00:56,000 --> 00:00:57,560
Your teacher is right.

15
00:00:57,680 --> 00:00:59,160
You are a student right now.

16
00:00:59,160 --> 00:01:01,020
You should focus on your studies.

17
00:01:01,080 --> 00:01:03,160
I am studying for exams on my own.

18
00:01:03,720 --> 00:01:06,000
Then you still want to continue live streaming?

19
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:06,960
That won't do.

20
00:01:07,280 --> 00:01:09,400
Girls shouldn't show their faces in public.

21
00:01:09,400 --> 00:01:11,160
What era is this?

22
00:01:11,560 --> 00:01:14,000
I definitely have my own reasons for wanting to do it.

23
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:15,600
It's the same in any era.

24
00:01:15,600 --> 00:01:17,730
This is also considering your future.

25
00:01:17,800 --> 00:01:19,880
I will take charge of my own future.

26
00:01:20,360 --> 00:01:22,240
Why can't I get through to you?

27
00:01:22,240 --> 00:01:23,039
Hey, Meixia.

28
00:01:23,039 --> 00:01:25,560
Did we leave our fruit in the car?

29
00:01:26,080 --> 00:01:27,160
I'll go get it.

30
00:01:27,320 --> 00:01:28,320
Go get it quickly.

31
00:01:31,960 --> 00:01:32,560
Hey.

32
00:01:32,560 --> 00:01:33,360
Zixi.

33
00:01:33,640 --> 00:01:34,970
Are you dating someone?

34
00:01:35,640 --> 00:01:36,960
No.

35
00:01:37,800 --> 00:01:38,759
You wouldn't dare

36
00:01:38,759 --> 00:01:41,000
talk back to your mom like this before.

37
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:43,200
I'm doing this

38
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:44,930
because I have my own thoughts.

39
00:01:45,039 --> 00:01:47,680
I wanted to take you to see my live streaming room.

40
00:01:47,680 --> 00:01:48,880
Live streaming room?

41
00:01:48,880 --> 00:01:49,600
Sure.

42
00:01:49,720 --> 00:01:50,880
I want to go see it.

43
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:55,080
But my senior should still be tidying up.

44
00:01:55,360 --> 00:01:56,440
He's there too?

45
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:01,000
Then we really have to go.

46
00:02:01,520 --> 00:02:02,360
Ha.

47
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:14,240
Senior, this is my dad.

48
00:02:14,520 --> 00:02:16,050
This is my senior, An Yufan.

49
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:17,360
You play music?

50
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:18,560
Hello, sir.

51
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:20,560
I used to be in a band too.

52
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:22,540
Have you heard of the Hudong Band?

53
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:26,160
Oh, that really famous band.

54
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:27,329
I've heard of it.

55
00:02:27,480 --> 00:02:28,920
Zixi told you, right?

56
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:30,160
Back then, her mom

57
00:02:30,320 --> 00:02:32,960
fell for me because I played in a band.

58
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:34,280
She was crazy about me.

59
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:38,760
I didn't expect you to be so handsome

60
00:02:38,760 --> 00:02:40,360
and play in a band.

61
00:02:40,920 --> 00:02:41,880
At school,

62
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:44,640
you must be very popular with the girls.

63
00:02:45,480 --> 00:02:47,680
Sir, I don't play music anymore.

64
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:48,920
You don't play anymore?

65
00:02:48,920 --> 00:02:50,000
Why?

66
00:02:53,320 --> 00:02:54,920
There's a situation at home.

67
00:02:58,079 --> 00:02:58,880
Oh,

68
00:02:59,600 --> 00:03:02,560
where did those two go?

69
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:04,320
Let me help you with that.

70
00:03:04,480 --> 00:03:05,920
Oh, great.

71
00:03:05,920 --> 00:03:07,480
Thank you for the trouble.

72
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:09,480
It's quite heavy.

73
00:03:09,480 --> 00:03:10,360
Yes, it is.

74
00:03:10,360 --> 00:03:11,880
Where are you taking this?

75
00:03:11,880 --> 00:03:13,000
Mr. Wang's office.

76
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:14,360
Mr. Wang?

77
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:15,680
From the journalism department?

78
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:16,560
Yes.

79
00:03:17,079 --> 00:03:18,010
He's my advisor.

80
00:03:18,120 --> 00:03:19,800
Then you must know our Zixi.

81
00:03:22,760 --> 00:03:24,280
We're classmates.

82
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:27,280
Really? I'd like to ask you something.

83
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:28,720
How is our Zixi

84
00:03:28,720 --> 00:03:31,480
usually doing in class?

85
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,360
Zixi?

86
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:34,720
She is very nice.

87
00:03:35,040 --> 00:03:37,840
Positive, sunny, optimistic,

88
00:03:38,079 --> 00:03:39,680
and full of energy.

89
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:41,200
Hahaha.

90
00:03:41,200 --> 00:03:42,320
Is that so?

91
00:03:42,480 --> 00:03:43,600
I didn't expect your family

92
00:03:43,600 --> 00:03:45,760
to have gone through such a huge tragedy.

93
00:03:45,760 --> 00:03:47,160
After that, I was no longer in the mood

94
00:03:47,160 --> 00:03:48,280
to make music.

95
00:03:48,480 --> 00:03:52,480
Don't worry. People have to suffer setbacks to grow.

96
00:03:52,920 --> 00:03:55,360
It was also because Zixi got hurt back then

97
00:03:55,640 --> 00:03:57,480
that I completely left the band.

98
00:03:57,480 --> 00:03:58,280
Ah.

99
00:03:59,200 --> 00:04:00,680
When you were 6 years old,

100
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:01,920
you hit your head

101
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:03,080
and fell into a coma.

102
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:05,200
Your mom and I were worried sick.

103
00:04:06,160 --> 00:04:08,680
I really can't remember clearly what happened back then.

104
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:09,800
You were still young then.

105
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:11,280
It was because of this

106
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:13,880
that I decided not to go out anymore.

107
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:16,680
Wasn't it because you had too many female fans?

108
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:17,480
Haha.

109
00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:19,279
I wish I did.

110
00:04:19,279 --> 00:04:21,959
Too bad there are so few people with good taste.

111
00:04:21,959 --> 00:04:22,920
Haha.

112
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:25,280
I heard from Zixi

113
00:04:25,280 --> 00:04:27,410
that you helped her find the evidence.

114
00:04:27,760 --> 00:04:29,800
Actually, Zixi solved it herself.

115
00:04:30,320 --> 00:04:31,560
Oh, did she?

116
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:35,920
Hello?

117
00:04:36,080 --> 00:04:37,200
Where did you guys go?

118
00:04:37,200 --> 00:04:38,720
I booked a restaurant. Let's go out to eat.

119
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:39,880
Okay, I got it.

120
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:41,200
We'll be right there.

121
00:04:42,520 --> 00:04:44,320
Zixi's mom arranged dinner.

122
00:04:44,320 --> 00:04:46,080
Let's go eat together.

123
00:04:49,280 --> 00:04:51,340
Your teacher is busy with something.

124
00:04:51,640 --> 00:04:53,600
Let's have a meal with just our family.

125
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:56,159
Just us family.

126
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:01,640
Why are you here?

127
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:04,280
If you can come, why can't I?

128
00:05:06,760 --> 00:05:07,680
This is

129
00:05:07,680 --> 00:05:10,240
Xiaoxi's classmate, Liang Chen.

130
00:05:10,640 --> 00:05:13,240
He has good grades, good character,

131
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:14,400
Hello, Uncle.

132
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:15,800
and an even better family background.

133
00:05:15,800 --> 00:05:17,440
Hey, don't mess around.

134
00:05:17,960 --> 00:05:19,200
Oh, right.

135
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:22,240
I heard you like to drink.

136
00:05:22,440 --> 00:05:23,920
There's nothing particularly good nearby.

137
00:05:23,920 --> 00:05:26,000
Good, very thoughtful of you.

138
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:28,000
Uncle and Auntie, please have a seat first.

139
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:29,040
I'll go tell them to serve the dishes.

140
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:30,680
Okay, okay.

141
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:41,090
What do you want from me now?

142
00:05:41,520 --> 00:05:43,159
You have to help me.

143
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:45,720
The teacher told me to suspend my studies and wait for further notice at home.

144
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:47,280
I don't want to be expelled.

145
00:05:48,200 --> 00:05:49,800
It's no use coming to me.

146
00:05:50,840 --> 00:05:52,360
Because of this,

147
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:56,010
I have already been suspended by the school for investigation.

148
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:58,200
How could this happen?

149
00:05:58,560 --> 00:05:59,960
I should be asking you.

150
00:06:00,320 --> 00:06:02,360
Why would the teacher suspect me?

151
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:05,800
It must be An Yufan.

152
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:08,160
An Yufan?

153
00:06:08,960 --> 00:06:10,800
Yes, it's him and Yin Zixi.

154
00:06:11,480 --> 00:06:12,280
Last time.

155
00:06:15,240 --> 00:06:17,080
Wang Yu from the student council put you up to this, right?

156
00:06:17,080 --> 00:06:19,280
So what if he did?

157
00:06:20,280 --> 00:06:21,320
They asked me as soon as we met

158
00:06:21,320 --> 00:06:22,960
if you put me up to it.

159
00:06:23,160 --> 00:06:23,880
It must be them

160
00:06:23,880 --> 00:06:25,200
who reported to the school.

161
00:06:25,200 --> 00:06:26,440
Didn't you let it slip?

162
00:06:26,440 --> 00:06:27,800
It wasn't me.

163
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:29,640
I really didn't say anything.

164
00:06:29,840 --> 00:06:31,100
You have to believe me.

165
00:06:31,200 --> 00:06:32,400
You have to help me.

166
00:06:32,760 --> 00:06:33,560
Got it.

167
00:06:43,520 --> 00:06:44,600
Look at your classmate.

168
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:46,460
Passed out after just two drinks.

169
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:48,409
Come on, let's have another drink.

170
00:06:48,520 --> 00:06:49,760
Okay.

171
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:53,040
Ah.

172
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:54,040
Tonight is so fun.

173
00:06:54,200 --> 00:06:55,880
Speaking of the past,

174
00:06:55,880 --> 00:06:57,280
there is no end to it.

175
00:06:57,280 --> 00:06:58,080
Hahaha.

176
00:06:58,080 --> 00:06:59,440
Back then,

177
00:06:59,440 --> 00:07:01,640
my band had so many female fans.

178
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:03,680
Don't tell Xiaoxi.

179
00:07:03,840 --> 00:07:05,840
Hey, let's have another drink.

180
00:07:10,960 --> 00:07:13,200
Hey, where did you two just go?

181
00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:15,360
I was just getting to the good part.

182
00:07:15,360 --> 00:07:17,090
Xixi went with me to get the car.

183
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:18,640
Dad is really something.

184
00:07:18,640 --> 00:07:20,080
He can't stop once he starts drinking.

185
00:07:20,080 --> 00:07:22,680
Getting older brings more problems.

186
00:07:23,080 --> 00:07:24,200
You don't, Mom.

187
00:07:24,400 --> 00:07:26,120
Mom is still young.

188
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:27,600
Ah.

189
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:28,840
Xixi.

190
00:07:28,840 --> 00:07:30,960
Something suddenly came up at the company for tomorrow.

191
00:07:30,960 --> 00:07:33,320
I won't be able to celebrate your birthday with you.

192
00:07:33,320 --> 00:07:34,280
It's fine, Dad.

193
00:07:34,880 --> 00:07:35,680
Birthday?

194
00:07:35,760 --> 00:07:37,760
Hey, this classmate is awake.

195
00:07:40,159 --> 00:07:41,360
He fell asleep again.

196
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:44,200
He drank too much today. Haha.

197
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:48,760
Uncle, we've arrived at the school.

198
00:07:49,320 --> 00:07:49,960
Oh.

199
00:07:49,960 --> 00:07:50,920
Xixi,

200
00:07:51,080 --> 00:07:53,720
take good care of yourself when you get back to school.

201
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:54,480
Yeah.

202
00:08:19,880 --> 00:08:21,540
Happy birthday, my daughter.

203
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:23,080
We came in a hurry.

204
00:08:23,160 --> 00:08:25,760
This gift was picked out by us at the last minute.

205
00:08:25,760 --> 00:08:26,920
Hope you like it.

206
00:08:38,679 --> 00:08:40,799
Mom, have you arrived home?

207
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:41,919
We just arrived.

208
00:08:41,919 --> 00:08:42,980
Hey, don't grab it.

209
00:08:43,880 --> 00:08:47,080
Daughter, those two male classmates are both pursuing you, right?

210
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:48,880
No.

211
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:50,960
Dad, you haven't sobered up yet.

212
00:08:51,120 --> 00:08:52,000
Really?

213
00:08:52,720 --> 00:08:53,760
Zixi,

214
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:55,880
you like that An Yufan, right?

215
00:08:55,880 --> 00:08:56,880
Mom.

216
00:08:57,560 --> 00:08:59,480
It's normal to fall in love in college.

217
00:08:59,480 --> 00:09:00,960
I'm not that rigid.

218
00:09:01,880 --> 00:09:04,600
On the way back, I thought for a long time.

219
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:07,930
I don't support you doing live streaming,

220
00:09:08,280 --> 00:09:10,760
because I'm worried about you being alone outside,

221
00:09:10,760 --> 00:09:13,080
with no one to take care of you or help you.

222
00:09:13,360 --> 00:09:14,920
But I've figured it out.

223
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:17,260
People will always encounter setbacks.

224
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:19,680
Your life only belongs to you.

225
00:09:20,680 --> 00:09:22,240
As long as it's your decision,

226
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:23,880
I will support you.

227
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:26,400
Thank you, Mom.

228
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:28,640
You are my daughter, after all.

229
00:09:28,640 --> 00:09:31,240
Take good care of yourself at school.

230
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:32,160
Yeah.

231
00:09:32,480 --> 00:09:33,480
You too.

232
00:09:56,120 --> 00:09:57,880
Casting Director Xi Chongjing

233
00:09:57,920 --> 00:09:59,840
Props Assistant Li Kunxiao

234
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:01,760
Production Vehicle Yi Mingle

235
00:10:01,800 --> 00:10:03,720
Yitong.
